        "TileImage": "$($repository fa0b9f07-d667-48d2-99c0-c5ee905fa973).Image",
        "Description": "Now that the staff at Dartmoor are all fully vaccinated, they want to party like it’s 1975 with a wild key party. Not everyone is invited though. Eliminate anyone with a key over the age of 35 so they don’t crash the party and ruin everyone’s fun. As the staff collectively funded this contract, you should try to avoid harming them if at all possible, but you&apos;re the expert, 47.",
